rs, /bin/rs.sh
alias: 'rs', 'redstone'

Control and inspect redstone on
any of the six sides.

Usage:
  rs                       all sides
  rs get <side>            on/level
  rs on|off <side>         set state
  rs set <side> <0..15>    analog
  rs pulse <side> [secs]   pulse
  rs bundled <side>        bundled
